OL,3,CDemand for English lessons
OL,4,C'overwhelms' NI system for foreign
OL,5,Cnationals
OL,7,FBy Sadeq Al-Wesabi
OL,9,FThere have been calls for an
OL,10,Foverarching strategy to help foreign
OL,11,Fnationals lean English as demand for
OL,12,Fclasses far outstrips supply.
OL,14,FThe Stormont department responsible
OL,15,Fsaid the system has been "overwhelmed"
OL,16,Fby demand.
OL,18,FOne campaigner said increasing the
OL,19,Fnumber of classes would help people
OL,20,Fintegrate better into Northern Ireland
OL,21,Fsociety.
