OL,7,FSandy Webb, training and education co-
OL,8,Fordinator at Donegall Pass Community
OL,9,FForum in Belfast, described the
OL,10,Fsituation regarding English for
OL,11,FSpeakers of Other Languages (ESOL) as
OL,12,Fdire.
OL,14,F"There's no overarching ESOL strategy
OL,15,Fin Northern Ireland, and it's a real
OL,16,Fminefield.
