OL,7,F"People are frustrated, stuck on huge
OL,8,Fwaiting lists for Belfast Met's
OL,9,Fcourses, struggling with online
OL,10,Fapplications, and if they don't get
OL,11,Fin, they're back to square one the
OL,12,Fnext year. It's a cycle that stops
OL,13,Fthem from learning English and affects
OL,14,Ftheir whole lives," she said.
OL,16,F"Community-based classes are so
OL,17,Fimportant, especially for women or
OL,18,Frefugees who can't afford buses to big
OL,19,Fcolleges like Millfield, where classes
OL,20,Fare packed."
