OL,10,FSandy pointed to a missed opportunity
OL,11,Ffor Northern Ireland to lead in
OL,12,Flanguage integration.
OL,14,F"Since 2015, we've missed the chance
OL,15,Fto be a showcase for integrating
OL,16,Fpeople through language," she said,
OL,17,Femphasising the need for a cohesive
OL,18,Fapproach to address the growing demand.
