OL,7,FIn 2023, the forum published 'Language
OL,8,FMatters', a report supported by
OL,9,Fresearch from Dr Donna Kernaghan,
OL,10,Fwhich examined ESOL provision by
OL,11,Fcommunity groups in south Belfast. The
OL,12,Fstudy revealed that community
OL,13,Forganisations rely heavily on
OL,14,Fvolunteers due to limited funding.
OL,16,FAhmed Al-Hattami is one volunteer
OL,17,Fteaching English in Londonderry.
