OL,7,FAs soon as he arrived in the city in
OL,8,Flate 2024, he noticed a huge gap in
OL,9,Fnumber of English teachers and began
OL,10,Flooking for a voluntary role where he
OL,11,Fcould support the migrant community
OL,12,Fand make use of his English teaching
OL,13,Fskills.
OL,15,F"It brings me great satisfaction to
OL,16,Fsee how many people benefit from the
OL,17,FEnglish classes I provide. I have now
OL,18,Fcompleted a full year in a 100%
OL,19,Fvoluntary role since November 2024,"
OL,20,Fhe said.
