OL,7,F"My motivation to volunteer comes from
OL,8,Fa genuine passion for helping others
OL,9,Fand being there for people who are in
OL,10,Fneed. The North West Migrant Forum has
OL,11,Fbeen the perfect environment for this
OL,12,Fwork."
OL,14,FAhmed also volunteers as an
OL,15,Finterpreter, accompanying people to
OL,16,Fhospitals and GP appointments, and
