OL,7,F"I hope to continue bridging gaps,
OL,8,Fempowering individuals and helping
OL,9,Fthem integrate with dignity and
OL,10,Fconfidence."
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland's shortage of ESOL
OL,13,Fcourses leaves many newcomers facing
OL,14,Flengthy waits and limited access,
OL,15,Fmaking it harder for them to learn
OL,16,FEnglish, integrate and find jobs.
OL,18,FSara Abdullah, from Sudan, waited over
OL,19,F14 months to secure a place in English
OL,20,Flanguage classes at Belfast Met.
