OL,7,FThe Department for the Economy said
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland's six further
OL,9,Feducation colleges, the largest
OL,10,Fproviders of accredited ESOL courses,
OL,11,Foffer free classes to vulnerable
OL,12,Fgroups, including refugees and asylum
OL,13,Fseekers, as part of the cross-
OL,14,Fdepartmental Refugee Integration
OL,15,FStrategy.
OL,17,FIn the 2023/24 academic year, the
OL,18,Fcolleges enrolled 2,125 ESOL learners
OL,19,Facross 4,280 enrolments.
