OL,7,FA spokesperson from the Department for
OL,8,Fthe Economy told UTV: "Provision is
OL,9,Fdemand-led, based on available
OL,10,Fresources and funding."
OL,12,F"The rising number of non-English
OL,13,Fspeakers has overwhelmed the system,
OL,14,Fparticularly at Belfast Met, which
OL,15,Ffaces the highest demand due to its
OL,16,Fcentral location. This has led to long
OL,17,Fwaiting lists," said the spokesperson.
