OL,7,FAs of the end of October 2025, there
OL,8,Fwere approximately 400 individuals on
OL,9,Fwaiting lists for ESOL provision
OL,10,Facross the FE colleges.
OL,12,FThe spokesperson added that, to
OL,13,Faddress the issue, the Minister for
OL,14,Fthe Economy recently opened a new ESOL
OL,15,FUnit at Belfast Met, providing a
OL,16,Ftailored environment with access to
OL,17,Fcareer advice and student funding
OL,18,Fsupport.
