OL,7,FDespite this, the lack of a broader
OL,8,Fstrategy continues to hinder progress.
OL,9,FCommunity-based efforts are filling
OL,10,Fthe gap, often by using dedicated
OL,11,Fvolunteers.
OL,13,FOver the past few years, Northern
OL,14,FIreland has received thousands of
OL,15,Fmigrants asylum seekers, putting more
OL,16,Fpressure on the ESOL centres which
OL,17,Fprovide free-language courses.
