OL,7,FAdvocates like Sandy saw potential for
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland to become a model for
OL,9,Finclusive language education given its
OL,10,Fsmall size and community.
OL,12,F"It is widely accepted that people who
OL,13,Faren't proficient in English are more
OL,14,Flikely to be unemployed, have low pay,
OL,15,Fhave low confidence and self-belief,
OL,16,Fand poor community bonds and be
OL,17,Fvulnerable to loneliness and
OL,18,Fisolation," she said.
